;;; Tests for SRFI-267.
;;;
;;; These were adapter from the original test suite.
;;;
;;; Indentation and syntax highlighting will naturally be broken after some tests, because
;;; things like #"delim"abc"def"delim" will confuse editors.
;;;
;;; Below, for reference, the original 'test' procedure:
;;;
